The paper deals with place categorization in robot vision, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed approach involves deep learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
